93
00:06:02.659 --> 00:06:03.859
Ya, pak.

94
00:06:03.859 --> 00:06:06.659
Tuan Hiramatsu juga berulang kali juga memukul sang pembunuhnya

95
00:06:06.659 --> 00:06:09.059
