146
00:08:25.459 --> 00:08:28.259
Sato dan Chiba, tanyakan orang-orang di sekitar sini.

147
00:08:28.259 --> 00:08:29.259
-Siap, pak. -Siap, pak.

148
00:08:29.259 --> 00:08:31.459
Shiratori, jaga mesin fotokopinya

149
00:08:31.459 --> 00:08:34.359
